# model:
# model:ir.model.fields,help:account_tax_python.field_account_tax__amount_type
#, []
msgid ""
"\n"
"    - Group of Taxes: The tax is a set of sub taxes.\n"
"    - Fixed: The tax amount stays the same whatever the price.\n"
"    - Percentage: The tax amount is a % of the price:\n"
"        e.g 100 * (1 + 10%) = 110 (not price included)\n"
"        e.g 110 / (1 + 10%) = 100 (price included)\n"
"    - Percentage Tax Included: The tax amount is a division of the price:\n"
"        e.g 180 / (1 - 10%) = 200 (not price included)\n"
"        e.g 200 * (1 - 10%) = 180 (price included)\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    - Grupa poreza: Porez je skup pod-poreza.\n"
"    - Fiksni: Iznos poreza ostaje isti bez obzira na cijenu.\n"
"    - Postotak: Iznos poreza je % cijene:\n"
"        npr. 100 * (1 + 10%) = 110 (cijena bez poreza)\n"
"        npr. 110 / (1 + 10%) = 100 (cijena s porezom)\n"
"    - Postotak porez uključen: Iznos poreza je dio cijene:\n"
"        npr. 180 / (1 - 10%) = 200 (cijena bez poreza)\n"
"        npr. 200 * (1 - 10%) = 180 (cijena s porezom)\n"
"        "

# model:
# model:ir.model.fields,help:account_tax_python.field_account_tax__formula
#, []
msgid ""
"Compute the amount of the tax.\n"
"\n"
":param base: float, actual amount on which the tax is applied\n"
":param price_unit: float\n"
":param quantity: float\n"
":param product: A object representing the product\n"
msgstr ""
"Izračunaj iznos poreza.\n"
"\n"
":param base: float, stvarni iznos na koji se primjenjuje porez\n"
":param price_unit: float\n"
":param quantity: float\n"
":param product: Objekt koji predstavlja proizvod\n"

